      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="0043_FL81799538"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1<unclear>1</unclear>. 1<unclear>2.</unclear> 911</date>.</seg></seg><seg><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></seg><salute>lieber Doctor Zweig,</salute></opener><p>wollen Sie morgen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03790-1"/><date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03790-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="Cf" target="1911-12-12"/>.</note> bei uns
               nachtmahlen, (<time>8 Uhr</time>),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o würds uns<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr freuen.</p><p><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11561">Hagemann</rs></hi>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>owie einige <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wiener</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2167 #pmb13055 #pmb10863" subtype="implied" cert="medium">Freunde</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind bei uns. Um g<unclear>enaue</unclear>
               Antwort wird gebeten.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t grüßt Sie<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
